{
  "atk-s0301a0:0": " Namo tassa bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa",
  "atk-s0301a0:1": "Saṃyuttanikāye",
  "atk-s0301a0:2": "Sagāthāvagga-aṭṭhakathā",
  "atk-s0301a0:3": "Ganthārambhakathā",
  "atk-s0301a0:4": "Karuṇāsītalahadayaṃ , paññāpajjotavihatamohatamaṃ;",
  "atk-s0301a0:5": "Sanarāmaralokagaruṃ, vande sugataṃ gativimuttaṃ.",
  "atk-s0301a0:6": "Buddhopi buddhabhāvaṃ, bhāvetvā ceva sacchikatvā ca;",
  "atk-s0301a0:7": "Yaṃ upagato gatamalaṃ, vande tamanuttaraṃ dhammaṃ.",
  "atk-s0301a0:8": "Sugatassa orasānaṃ, puttānaṃ mārasenamathanānaṃ;",
  "atk-s0301a0:9": "Aṭṭhannampi samūhaṃ, sirasā vande ariyasaṅghaṃ.",
  "atk-s0301a0:10": "Iti me pasannamatino, ratanattayavandanāmayaṃ puññaṃ;",
  "atk-s0301a0:11": "Yaṃ suvihatantarāyo, hutvā tassānubhāvena.",
  "atk-s0301a0:12": "Saṃyuttavaggapaṭimaṇḍitassa, saṃyuttaāgamavarassa;",
  "atk-s0301a0:13": "Buddhānubuddhasaṃvaṇṇitassa, ñāṇappabhedajananassa.",
  "atk-s0301a0:14": "Atthappakāsanatthaṃ, aṭṭhakathā ādito vasisatehi;",
  "atk-s0301a0:15": "Pañcahi yā saṅgītā, anusaṅgītā ca pacchāpi.",
  "atk-s0301a0:16": "Sīhaḷadīpaṃ pana ābhatātha, vasinā mahāmahindena;",
  "atk-s0301a0:17": "Ṭhapitā sīhaḷabhāsāya, dīpavāsīnamatthāya.",
  "atk-s0301a0:18": "Apanetvāna tatohaṃ, sīhaḷabhāsaṃ manoramaṃ bhāsaṃ;",
  "atk-s0301a0:19": "Tantinayānucchavikaṃ, āropento vigatadosaṃ.",
  "atk-s0301a0:20": "Samayaṃ avilomento, therānaṃ theravaṃsadīpānaṃ;",
  "atk-s0301a0:21": "Sunipuṇavinicchayānaṃ, mahāvihāre nivāsīnaṃ.",
  "atk-s0301a0:22": "Hitvā punappunāgata-matthaṃ, atthaṃ pakāsayissāmi;",
  "atk-s0301a0:23": "Sujanassa ca tuṭṭhatthaṃ, ciraṭṭhitatthañca dhammassa.",
  "atk-s0301a0:24": "Sāvatthipabhūtīnaṃ, nagarānaṃ vaṇṇanā katā heṭṭhā;",
  "atk-s0301a0:25": "Saṅgītīnaṃ dvinnaṃ, yā me atthaṃ vadantena.",
  "atk-s0301a0:26": "Vitthāravasena sudaṃ, vatthūni ca yāni tattha vuttāni;",
  "atk-s0301a0:27": "Tesampi na idha bhiyyo, vitthārakathaṃ karissāmi.",
  "atk-s0301a0:28": "Suttānaṃ pana atthā, na vinā vatthūhi ye pakāsanti;",
  "atk-s0301a0:29": "Tesaṃ pakāsanatthaṃ, vatthūnipi dassayissāmi.",
  "atk-s0301a0:30": "Sīlakathā dhutadhammā, kammaṭṭhānāni ceva sabbāni;",
  "atk-s0301a0:31": "Cariyāvidhānasahito, jhānasamāpattivitthāro.",
  "atk-s0301a0:32": "Sabbā ca abhiññāyo, paññāsaṅkalananicchayo ceva;",
  "atk-s0301a0:33": "Khandhādhātāyatanindriyāni, ariyāni ceva cattāri.",
  "atk-s0301a0:34": "Saccāni paccayākāradesanā, suparisuddhanipuṇanayā;",
  "atk-s0301a0:35": "Avimuttatantimaggā, vipassanābhāvanā ceva.",
  "atk-s0301a0:36": "Iti pana sabbaṃ yasmā, visuddhimagge mayā suparisuddhaṃ;",
  "atk-s0301a0:37": "Vuttaṃ tasmā bhiyyo, na taṃ idha vicārayissāmi.",
  "atk-s0301a0:38": "‘‘Majjhe visuddhimaggo, esa catunnampi āgamānañhi;",
  "atk-s0301a0:39": "Ṭhatvā pakāsayissati, tattha yathābhāsitamatthaṃ’’.",
  "atk-s0301a0:40": "Icceva kato tasmā, tampi gahetvāna saddhimetāya;",
  "atk-s0301a0:41": "Aṭṭhakathāya vijānatha, saṃyuttavinissitaṃ atthanti."
}